      "text": "1. caching:  cpu fetches information in byte in  its register(memory), can  direct access  those \n       array's element via index which is very fast( no need to travel to ram)\n",
      "fontSize": 15.882801387133432,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. caching:  cpu fetches information in byte in  its register(memory), can  direct access  those \n       array's element via index which is very fast( no need to travel to ram)\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
